snippet.title: WHO... or WHAT Killed Project Zorgo?
snippet.description:
The Spy Ninjas saw Agent Peters on the news! He's been captured and placed next to the Project Zorgo Leader's grave! Who did it!? The news reveals that there is more video footage, but the news station won't show it all! The Spy Ninjas need to see the rest of the footage so they can identify who the PZ Killer is. They decide to go to the news station and get the footage! At the TV station, the Spy Ninjas meet some weird people and realize there are more people looking to find and destroy the footage. What are on these tapes? It must be something really powerful or scary! Thank you for watching my funny entertainment comedy adventure vlog videos in 2021!
